        <scopecontent id="ref18">
            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>This collection contains newclippings about the hunger strike, the diary Boone kept during hunger strike, an audiotape of Sonia Johnson's speech at NCSU, photographs, printouts of Doonesbury cartoons, memorabilia, and a few other documents.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <userestrict id="ref21">
